    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

  wd:Q2926117 wdt:P19 ?birthplace1.
  ?birthplace1 wdt:P131* ?state.

  ?birthplace2 wdt:P131* ?state.
    
  ?state wdt:P31 wd:Q35657.
}

question.string: How many spouses do head of states have on average?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT (AVG(?count) AS ?averageSpouses)
WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256.
  ?country p:P35 ?statement.
  ?statement ps:P35 ?headOfState.
  ?headOfState wdt:P26 ?spouse.

  {
    SELECT ?headOfState (COUNT(DISTINCT ?spouse) AS ?count)
    WHERE {
      ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256.
      ?country p:P35 ?positionStatement.
      ?positionStatement ps:P35 ?headOfState.
      OPTIONAL { ?headOfState wdt:P26 ?spouse. }
    }
    GROUP BY ?headOfState
  }
}

SELECT ?year ?lifeExpectancy ?previousLifeExpectancy
WHERE {
  wd:Q794 p:P2250 ?lifeExpectancyStatement .
  ?lifeExpectancyStatement pq:P585 ?date ;
                           ps:P2250 ?lifeExpectancy .
  FILTER(YEAR(?date) > 1999)
  OPTIONAL {
    ?prevStatement ps:P2250 ?previousLifeExpectancy ;
                   pq:P585 ?prevDate .
    FILTER(?prevDate < ?date)
  }
  FILTER(?lifeExpectancy > ?previousLifeExpectancy)
}
ORDER BY ?date

question.string: What event killed the most people in the years 1910 to 1920?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?event ?eventLabel (MAX(?deaths) as ?maxDeaths) WHERE {
  ?event wdt:P31 wd:Q1190554. 
  ?event wdt:P1120 ?deaths.
  ?event wdt:P580 ?start_date.
  ?event wdt:P582 ?end_date.
  FILTER(?start_date >= "1910-01-01"^^xsd:dateTime && ?end_date <= "1920-12-31"^^xsd:dateTime)
  SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?event ?eventLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?maxDeaths)
LIMIT 1

SELECT (SUM(?revenue) AS ?totalRevenue)

  }
}

LIMIT 3

}

LIMIT 1

question.string: Did Germany have a population growth of at least 1% since 2010?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?year2010Pop ?latestYear ?latestYearPop WHERE {
  wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?pop2010Statement.
  ?pop2010Statement pq:P585 ?date2010.
  ?pop2010Statement ps:P1082 ?year2010Pop.
  FILTER(YEAR(?date2010) = 2010)
  
  wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?latestPopStatement.
  ?latestPopStatement pq:P585 ?dateLatest.
  ?latestPopStatement ps:P1082 ?latestYearPop.
  FILTER(YEAR(?dateLatest) > 2010)
  
  BIND(YEAR(?dateLatest) AS ?latestYear)
}
